===Proper noun===
'''Cairbre Nia Fer'''

# (''Irish mythology'') The king of Tara during the [[Ulster Cycle]] of [[Irish]] [[mythology]], who was killed by [[Cúchulainn]] in the Battle of Ros na Ríg.  Son-in-law of [[Conchobar mac Nessa]] and cousin-in-law of [[Conall Cernach]].  Husband of [[Fedelm Noíchrothach]]. Father of [[Erc]] and [[Achall]].

